Cell[CellGroupData[{

Cell["Notes", "Section",ExpressionUUID->"a41c6e2b-23e1-4078-a8fa-36b400f6c038"],

Cell["\<\
The low-order `A1..C4` basis is the actual master-integral derivation layer. \
The closed M13 and M22 sector formulas are then the package-facing reduced \
contractions built from that basis plus the real-space Gaussian kernels. On \
the current local validation pass the Gaussian sector subset closes exactly, \
while the low-order coefficient `B2` stays nonzero against the CLASS-PT \
appendix transcription and some heavier exact simplifications can time out \
depending on the chosen `TimeConstrained` budget.\
\>", "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.9853337231222258`*^9, 
  3.985333724010244*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"933041e5-7913-4380-ac22-\
8f63cdc37d43"]
}, Open  ]]
}, Open  ]]
},
